    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Group of studies in the Middle Ages constituting the higher division of the seven liberal arts and consisting of arithmetic, music, geometry, and astronomy.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
